title: The Linux Action Show! Season 8 Episode 3 - OGG
description:
This week on, The Linux Action Show!

We cover the exciting progress of KDE 4 - Then we give you the latest updates on the eeePC, and go over the specs of their newly announced laptop. We also cover some news that ought to make every listener quite pleased, Open Source Developers can make up to 40% more than commercials devs - we tell you why!

THEN -

We interview the founder of the Linux Mint project, PLUS - we take some of your questions!
All this week on, The Linux Action Show!
